org.eclipse.jgit.events.RepositoryEvent

  • RepositoryEventを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.eclipse.jgit.events
    Events and listener interfaces.
    org.eclipse.jgit.internal.storage.dfs
    Distributed file system based repository storage.
    org.eclipse.jgit.lib
    Core API for repository, config, refs, object database.

    • org.eclipse.jgit.eventsでのRepositoryEventの使用

      org.eclipse.jgit.eventsでのRepositoryEventのサブクラス 
      修飾子とタイプ クラスと説明
      class  ConfigChangedEvent
      Describes a change to one or more keys in the configuration.
      class  IndexChangedEvent
      Describes a change to one or more paths in the index file.
      class  RefsChangedEvent
      Describes a change to one or more references of a repository.
      RepositoryEvent型のパラメータを持つorg.eclipse.jgit.eventsのメソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      void ListenerList.dispatch(RepositoryEvent event)
      Dispatch an event to all interested listeners.

    • org.eclipse.jgit.internal.storage.dfsでのRepositoryEventの使用

      org.eclipse.jgit.internal.storage.dfsでのRepositoryEventのサブクラス 
      修飾子とタイプ クラスと説明
      class  BeforeDfsPackIndexLoadedEvent
      Describes the DfsPackFile just before its index is loaded.
      class  DfsPacksChangedEvent
      Describes a change to the list of packs in a DfsRepository.

    • org.eclipse.jgit.libでのRepositoryEventの使用
